Do not be a perfectionist.
 Anyone who wants to definitely create something great often does not create anything at all.  Anyone who just does his job well every day has a chance to create something great one day.

Creativity can be trained.
Yes, these are not muscles, but the ability to be creative can be increased in much the same way as the number of pushups. To do this, you need daily training, hard work and perseverance.  And who said that creating is easy?
